"title='EDR Tradecraft: Internals, Detection, Evasion & Advanced Researchg | DbgMan' description='Technical reference on modern EDR architecture, detection mechanisms, evasion techniques, and reverse-engineering methodology. Covers kernel callback APIs, file-system mini-filters, ETW providers, the four detection-engine model, syscall gates (FreshyCalls, RecycledGate, SysWhispers4, Acheron, Sysplant), sleep obfuscation (Ekko, FOLIAGE, DreamWalkers), call-stack spoofing (SilentMoonwalk, VulcanRaven), ETW-TI hardware-breakpoint bypass, patchless AMSI bypass via VEH, BYOVD against the vulnerable-driver blocklist, and the eight-phase EDR research methodology.' url='https://0xdbgman.github.io/posts/edr-internals-research-and-bypass/' language='en' keywords=None robots=None og_title='EDR Tradecraft: Internals, Detection, Evasion & Advanced Researchg' og_description='Technical reference on modern EDR architecture, detection mechanisms, evasion techniques, and reverse-engineering methodology. Covers kernel callback APIs, file-system mini-filters, ETW providers, the four detection-engine model, syscall gates (FreshyCalls, RecycledGate, SysWhispers4, Acheron, Sysplant), sleep obfuscation (Ekko, FOLIAGE, DreamWalkers), call-stack spoofing (SilentMoonwalk, VulcanRaven), ETW-TI hardware-breakpoint bypass, patchless AMSI bypass via VEH, BYOVD against the vulnerable-driver blocklist, and the eight-phase EDR research methodology.' og_url='https://0xdbgman.github.io/posts/edr-internals-research-and-bypass/' og_image='https://0xDbgMan.github.io/assets/img/edr-internals/backGround.png' og_audio=None og_determiner=None og_locale='en' og_locale_alternate=None og_site_name='DbgMan' og_video=None favicon='https://0xdbgman.github.io/assets/img/favicons/favicon-96x96.png' dc_terms_created=None dc_date_created=None dc_date=None dc_terms_type=None dc_type=None dc_terms_audience=None dc_terms_subject=None dc_subject=None dc_description=None dc_terms_keywords=None modified_time='2026-05-06T01:01